<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { background: #DC2626; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; }
    .content { padding: 20px; background: #f9fafb; border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px; }
    .button { display: inline-block; background: #DC2626; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; margin-top: 20px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1> LIVE NOW</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hi {{name}},</p>
      <p><strong>{{lectureTitle}}</strong> is starting now!</p>
      <p>Don't miss this live session. Click the button below to join instantly.</p>
      <a href="{{joinUrl}}" class="button">Join Live Lecture</a>
      <p>See you there!<br>The ClassCast Team</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>